Package InfrastructureManager.ModuleManagement

Interface ImmutablePlatformModule

All Known Implementing Classes:
AdvantEdgeModule, ConsoleModule, MatchMakingModule, MatchMakingNaiveModule, MatchMakingRandomModule, MatchMakingScoreBasedModule, NetworkModule, PlatformModule, RemoteExecutionModule, RESTModule, ScenarioModule, UtilityModule
public interface ImmutablePlatformModule
Interface for the different modules to implement to appear as read-only immutable objects
